--executive mode commands--
cls / ctrl+l == clear screen
application start = start an application
show application status ise == show all apps running
application stop = stop an application
? == help same like cisco routers and switches
set clock H:M:S:YYYY = set date and time
copy running-config startup-config == save
copy startup-config running-config == restore
show running-config == show all the configuration details
debug ? /debug all == show logs for debugging
undebug all == exit debugging mode 
reload == reboot
halt == shutdown
password == change password 
ping == ping 
traceroute == check routes to ip/domain
ssh == connect ssh to other machine
